{"tid":614744,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[星座] 魔羯女","createTime":"2018-04-02T19:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T01:04:34.000Z","uid":49401,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0e67090fbe568da087ba5e26e520cb0ffaa4474e","tid":614744,"uid":49401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T19:21:23.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n<br />\n  我同佢一齊一開始個陣大家都好熱情，情話會講，係朋友面前都會拖下手。<br />\n<br />\n  到依家過左半年，佢就開始越黎越冷，基本上講情話，佢就唔覆或都避左話題，係朋友面前亦都唔會再比我掂。<br />\n <br />\n  我有問過原因，佢就話係因為壓力大同唔開心。但我感覺就唔係咁。至少係對住我先冷淡。前個排仲嘈話分手，佢就好唔想，咁我都心軟，但過左日又打回原形。<br />\n<br />\n  咁係咪姐係代表佢心淡，或者已經唔鐘意我？我有問過佢就話我諗太多，但你地知啦，女仔係呢家野唔係好信得過。所以我應該放手？"},{"pid":"1e3630c9015e73d04088998d6f18a44bc3fafd7d","tid":614744,"uid":178303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T19:22:57.000Z","msg":"似騎牛搵馬"},{"pid":"d8d9fa63fee66f1d4d32d28291aa3511c134b42f","tid":614744,"uid":156853,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T19:23:47.000Z","msg":"其實關星座咩事？"},{"pid":"9670f3d198d8499aeb696e9f7baa3d19cab2961c","tid":614744,"uid":49401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1e3630c9015e73d04088998d6f18a44bc3fafd7d","tid":614744,"uid":178303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T19:22:57.000Z","msg":"似騎牛搵馬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T19:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢之前散左半年，我地就一齊左，"},{"pid":"e2790117782d4775e26bcf0b103eca41464d2de9","tid":614744,"uid":178303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9670f3d198d8499aeb696e9f7baa3d19cab2961c","tid":614744,"uid":49401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1e3630c9015e73d04088998d6f18a44bc3fafd7d","tid":614744,"uid":178303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T19:22:57.000Z","msg":"似騎牛搵馬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T19:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢之前散左半年，我地就一齊左，"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20